name: Ecodog
description: Ecodoge (EDOG) is a reflection token built on the Binance-smart-chain (BEP-20) with a Proof-of-Work (PoW) mechanism aimed at increasing the token value and volume with daily buybacks and rewards. Ecodoge (EDOG) is a recycling plant that can produce 6 Megawatts per hour of clean energy by recycling mixed domestic waste.
